<div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64" id="about">
  <h1 class="w3-center">The All Souls Procession Festivities</h1>
  <p class="w3-center"><em>Sean Orth, Sarah Briggs, Brianna Darling, Brianna Lewis</em>
  <br>
  All photos by Rebecca Noble</p>
  <div id="images_hz" div align="center">
  
<a href="#story1">
  <img src=http://i63.tinypic.com/57h4z.jpg>
</a>
<a href="#story2">
  <img src=http://i66.tinypic.com/i50x80.jpg>
</a>
<a href="#story3">
  <img src=http://i63.tinypic.com/kaln9y.jpg>
